title: Speed Academy's Dave Pratte and Peter Tarach
author: matt@thesmokingtire.com (Matt Farah & Zack Klapman)
itunes:title: Speed Academy's Dave Pratte and Peter Tarach
itunes:author: Matt Farah & Zack Klapman
itunes:summary:
Speed Academy is a website and YouTube channel all about building fast cars the right way. Hosted by Peter Tarach and Dave Pratte, the channel will teach you how to upgrade, tune, and swap your engine, the right way. We talk about wrenching in the rust belt, about Japanese car values, why K swaps are getting popular, their big sedan challenge, JDM legends build-off, and a lot more. Don't miss it!
